p.k: Proposals, plots and prostitutes combine for a comedy of errors on floor nine. Welcome to London's Hotel Zanzibar. Zanzibar (2018). Cast: Rory Kinnear, Hattie Morahan, Bill Paterson, Kevin Eldon, Tanya Franks, Marcia Warren, Reece Shearsmith, Steve Pemberton, Helen Monks, Jaygann Ayeh. Director: David Kerr.
